e classes of all the non-static data members of type array of class have trivial constructors  \n  \n## Requirements  \n **Header:** <type_traits>  \n  \n **Namespace:** std  \n  \n## See Also  \n [<type_traits>](../standard-library/type-traits.md)\n\n\n\n"}